
make roux with

 - 2 tbsp butter
 - 3 tbsp flour
 - 1 cup milk
 - 2/3 cup lager beer

simmer 1 minute
add
 - 1/2 tsp garlic powder
 - 1/4 tsp smoked papprika
 - 1/4 tsp salt
 - black pepper
slowly whisk in
 - 250 g grated cheddar
add 
 - 2 tsp whecestershire
 - 2 tsp dijon
 
 more than enough for soft pretzel batch from 500g flour
